  Locus:
    Page: 343
    Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Oneness
---
Through drying one person’s tears you are drying the whole
world’s tears. In making one lame person walk, you are helping every lame
person throughout the universe ... because the Group is never separated,
and always works through the contribution of each member to the whole.
